  <steps>
    <step order="1">Author `MockServiceClientFactory.cs` helper that creates a Moq'd `IOrganizationService` with configurable `Execute` / `Retrieve` / `RetrieveMultiple` responses.</step>
    <step order="2">Author `SavedQueryEndpointsTests.cs`: happy path for both endpoints; 403 with restricted-user mock; cache hit verified by counting ServiceClient calls (2 calls = 1 ServiceClient hit + 1 cache hit).</step>
    <step order="3">Author `MetadataEndpointTests.cs`: happy path; 403; cache hit; payload-size assertion (&lt;50KB for representative entity).</step>
    <step order="4">Author `FetchEndpointTests.cs`: happy path; 403 on read-deny; **cross-entity privilege bypass test** ‚Äî FetchXML with `&lt;link-entity name="restricted"&gt;` returns 403 even though caller has Read on primary entity; malformed FetchXML ‚Üí 400.</step>
    <step order="5">Author `RecordEndpointTests.cs`: happy path; 404 on missing record; 403; `$select` projection works.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet test tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/`; verify all pass.</step>
    <step order="7">Verify CI workflow includes integration tests (check `.github/workflows/sdap-ci.yml`).</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX (016 ‚úÖ).</step>
  </steps>

